{"tid":2005751,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港人已同政府達成共識","createTime":"2020-05-07T10:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T01:33:59.000Z","uid":222614,"like":12,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"93799c37c4254a8a8e9dceae73497e343f243641","tid":2005751,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:16:45.000Z","msg":"政府：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要黃圈定要政權？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要黃圈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪有黃圈就乜都得？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係，有黃圈就乜都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好，我幫你地推黃圈上神台，我會不時叫人寫文批評下黃圈，扮驚扮嬲，將黃圈嘅爆光率提升到最盡，等香港人覺得黃圈好重要，但你地<span style=\"color: red;\">必需放棄任何實際嘅手段令我交出我手中嘅政權</span>。同時，你地其他方面嘅權利我都會逐漸剝奪，你地會察覺到，但有黃圈做你地嘅麻醉藥，你地唔好反抗，做唔做到？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做得到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地要令香港人對黃圈嘅關注遠超過對立法會同社會公義嘅關注，做唔做到？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無問題！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至於呢個現狀可以維持幾耐，你地可以放心，只要威脅唔到我手中嘅政權，係我嘅控制下可以確保永續黃圈，我會繼續扮驚扮嬲畀假希望香港人，明唔明白？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明白！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 非常好，合作愉快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黃色經濟圈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf0ef26a2d5428b15d8190b4e221ad0885177a7","tid":2005751,"uid":137493,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1caf74a03eb14867a1362939641973da7f67fa","tid":2005751,"uid":59976,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:22:51.000Z","msg":"一早話黃藍經濟圈根本就係支共一手策劃既計劃啦，奈何連登仔就係咁易中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e1dcfa8e2c0e171371ddde034752b3ef85b30a","tid":2005751,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:23:18.000Z","msg":"信唔信以後嘅所謂抗爭就係黃同藍之間嘅一唱一和？<br />\n<br />\n大家睇住黎 ...."},{"pid":"0fa7332bea97d39eba51d1ec7179173e26d08933","tid":2005751,"uid":231583,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"黃圈係生活一部份，同出唔出黎抗爭根本無關係，唔遊行我都要消費要搭車要食飯，所以講呢d野無意思"},{"pid":"c80d78ec69152fc479653c21e18d025485078b93","tid":2005751,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:24:07.000Z","msg":"黃圈同政權邊輪到政府話比就比？"},{"pid":"c7f62c9275b0ac663723626fa4836931d57520b9","tid":2005751,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:25:38.000Z","msg":"分化陰謀論<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拉</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"aef46f3882bbaa7da8a1c5d3b4fd283e27ac25bf","tid":2005751,"uid":59297,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲濕鳩假對立+標題偷換概念<br />\n係咁打稻草人話香港人食黃店就抗爭完，又唔講依家仲有肺炎，仲有人搞緊好撚多戰線<br />\n唔好撚理佢啦"},{"pid":"2782e6f0be5592f333d010bc83edaa71bcdb0c64","tid":2005751,"